# 19 - Resume Tailor
# Customize a resume for a specific job

NAME resume-tailor
INPUT resume_file
INPUT job_description_file

GOAL parse "Read $resume_file and $job_description_file. List key requirements vs candidate skills."
GOAL match "Identify top 5 matches and top 3 gaps."
GOAL tailor "Adjust resume bullet points to emphasize matches. Don't fabricate experience."
GOAL output "Save tailored resume to tailored-resume.md. Brief cover letter (200 words) to cover-letter.md."

RUN tailor USING parse, match, tailor, output
